{"tid":647441,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈振盈：市場不明朗因素仍多","createTime":"2018-04-29T23:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T03:45:33.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"95bc172f11f2da7c781c9d4472e6399dd4b43f78","tid":647441,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T23:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430000237526-0430_00842_001_01b.jpg?20180430000400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430000237526-0430_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20180430000400&h=fe878495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈在東方產經「另類指標」專欄表示，上周港股走勢反覆，但始終未能突破上落市格局，而且波幅愈收愈窄。市場上充斥着負面因素，投資者最怕遇上不明朗的環境，因而傾向沽貨減磅為主。中美貿易戰未有緩和迹象，配合美國對中興通訊(00763)的制裁，以及對華為的調查，態度取向明顯不過。<br />\n<br />\n內地正式公布資管新規例，除了監管嚴謹之外，投資者的准入門檻亦大大提高。原來現時內地的理財產品總值，超逾100萬億元人民幣，確實驚人，難怪監管機構這般緊張去作出規範。相信條例一出，中資金融股的盈利前景必受影響。<br />\n<br />\n本周五一黃金周假期，A股兩日假期，港股只放周二，大方向等周三後便可確定。本周每日的股市走勢預測：<br />\n<br />\n周一(壬辰日)：天干屬水地支屬土，土剋水之局，市況反覆震盪。<br />\n<br />\n周二(癸巳日)：假期。<br />\n<br />\n周三(甲午日)：天干屬木地支屬火，木生火之局，走勢向好。<br />\n<br />\n周四(乙未日)：天干屬木地支屬土，木剋土之局，市況出現震盪。<br />\n<br />\n周五(丙申日)：天干屬火地支屬金，火剋金之局，地支巳申化水，先高後低。<br />\n<br />\n訊匯證券行政總裁 沈振盈(作者為註冊持牌人士)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180430/bkn-20180430000237526-0430_00842_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180430%2Fbkn-20180430000237526-0430_00842_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=17a8424f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180430/bkn-20180430000237526-0430_00842_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"7e5c8984413396bae0e2cb3ecbfec9d60926bd63","tid":647441,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T23:51:13.000Z","msg":"呢條傻鳩燈足十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb534ba977a0f65d1833158afac4dd42ac3a73d4","tid":647441,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7af6ed461b7d0bf17418f759186e14b38b7970","tid":647441,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/103719_80e067213e65c5f499b52a41848cc15d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F103719_80e067213e65c5f499b52a41848cc15d.jpg&h=cfb81573&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa31270393f07e545554fddd673268cc0f3ba2e7","tid":647441,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/103936_3984b487265369a0010007cc9726cd0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F103936_3984b487265369a0010007cc9726cd0e.png&h=90a5e262&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6050fb3747757139a740afe6a224b7ddbf30845","tid":647441,"uid":94860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"收到 allin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53890dfe037078ae5ba4eeff712c34d0ce198a02","tid":647441,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"華生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb73ea0cd595516b1954cccac3f62e7109fd7f9","tid":647441,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"佢除左星期3 有邊日唔係震盪"}]}